            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/mobile/smartphone">Smartphone</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>UsoNatsu for Switch, Pokemon Champions for mobile, etc.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><em><a title="Games > The Adventures of Elliot: The Millennium Tales [9 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales">The Adventures of Elliot: The Millennium Tales</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> is the highlight of this week’s Japanese video game releases. <span id="more-1059269"></span></p><p>Also due out this week are <em>UsoNatsu: The Summer Romance Bloomed From A Lie</em> for <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>,&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > Pokemon Champions [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/pokemon-champions">Pokemon Champions</a></em> for iOS and Android, and <em><a title="Games > EA Sports UFC 6 [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/ea-sports-ufc-6">EA Sports UFC 6</a></em> for PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series.</p><p>Get the full list of this week’s Japanese game releases below. It should be noted that <a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gematsu">Gematsu</a> will receive a small percentage of money from purchases made through <a title="Companies > Playasia" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/playasia">Play-Asia</a> links. You can also save five percent with our multi-use “<strong>GEMATSU2025</strong>” coupon code.</p><h2><span>Physical and Digital</span></h2><ul><li><em>The Adventures of Elliot: The Millennium Tales</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales-multi-language/13/70ivrt?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales-multi-language/13/70ivrz?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>) – Launching worldwide. Game-key card on Switch 2.<ul><li>North American Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales/13/70iw99?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales/13/70iw9b?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Xbox Series</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales/13/70iw9d?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>)</li><li>European Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales/13/70iw9j?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales/13/70iw9l?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Xbox Series</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales/13/70iw9n?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>)</li><li>Asian Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales-multi-language/13/70ivs1?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales-multi-language/13/70ivs3?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>)</li></ul><!-- AD: content -->
        </li><li><em>EA Sports UFC 6</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/ea-sports-ufc-6-multi-language/13/70jw3x?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>) – Launching worldwide.<ul><li>North American Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/ea-sports-ufc-6/13/70jw6b?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/ea-sports-ufc-6/13/70jw6f?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Xbox Series</a>)</li><li>European Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/ea-sports-ufc-6/13/70jw6h?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/ea-sports-ufc-6/13/70jw6j?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Xbox Series</a>)</li><li>Asian Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/ea-sports-ufc-6-multi-language/13/70jwbp?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>)</li></ul></li><li><em><a title="Games > inKONBINI: One Store. Many Stories. [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/inkonbini-one-store-many-stories">inKONBINI: One Store. Many Stories.</a></em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/inkonbini-one-store-many-stories-multi-language/13/70j9wr?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/inkonbini-one-store-many-stories-multi-language/13/70j9wt?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>) – Already available digitally worldwide.<ul><li>Limited Edition (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/inkonbini-one-store-many-stories-limited-edition-multi-language/13/70jot7?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/inkonbini-one-store-many-stories-limited-edition-multi-language/13/70jot9?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li></ul></li><li><em>Little Kitty Big City</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/little-kitty-big-city-multi-language/13/70jrar?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)