3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/the-cub">The Cub</a></em> (Xbox Series, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,418 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, PC [<a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/the-cub/9NSTG1KGXJK4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Demeo x Dungeons &amp; Dragons: Battlemarked [5 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/demeo-x-dungeons-dragons-battlemarked">Demeo x Dungeons &amp; Dragons: Battlemarked</a></em> (Switch 2) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Dialoop [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dialoop">Dialoop</a></em> (Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > #DRIVE Rally [5 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/drive-rally">#DRIVE Rally</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch) – Launching worldwide.<ul><li>North American Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/drive-rally/13/70joqb?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/drive-rally/13/70joql?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li><li>European Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/drive-rally-special-edition/13/70jor3?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/drive-rally-special-edition/13/70jor5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li></ul></li><li><em>EA Sports UFC 6</em> (Xbox Series) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Forgotlings [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/forgotlings">Forgotlings</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Junkster [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/junkster">Junkster</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, PC [Steam, <a href="http://xbox.com/en-us/games/store/junkster/9NZPKBFF0CV9" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Observer: System Redux</em> (Switch 2) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Parking Garage Rally Circuit" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/parking-garage-rally-circuit">Parking Garage Rally Circuit</a></em> (Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Pokemon Champions</em> (iOS, Android) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > R-Type Tactics I • II Cosmos [12 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/r-type-tactics-i-ii-cosmos">R-Type Tactics I • II Cosmos</a></em> (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2169930/RType_Tactics_I__II_Cosmos/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide alongside global console versions.<ul><li>North American Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/r-type-tactics-i-ii-cosmos-deluxe-edition/13/70ftk5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/r-type-tactics-i-ii-cosmos-deluxe-edition/13/70ftk1?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS4</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/r-type-tactics-i-ii-cosmos-deluxe-edition/13/70ftk7?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li><li>European Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/r-type-tactics-i-ii-cosmos-deluxe-edition/13/70g1tp?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/r-type-tactics-i-ii-cosmos-deluxe-edition/13/70g1tn?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS4</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/r-type-tactics-i-ii-cosmos-deluxe-edition/13/70g1tr?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li></ul></li><li><em>Shift at Midnight</em> (Xbox Series, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3722330/Shift_At_Midnight/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, Microsoft Store]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Soccer Kid Collection [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/soccer-kid-collection">Soccer Kid Collection</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, Xbox One, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4447890/Soccer_Kid_Collection_QUByte_Classics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/soccer-kid-collection-qubyte-classics/9PH89D469PMH" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Twisted <a title="Series > Fate [70 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/fate">Fate</a></em> (Xbox Series) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Zenless Zone Zero [34 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/zenless-zone-zero">Zenless Zone Zero</a></em> (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4162040/Zenless_Zone_Zero/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li></ul><p>The PlayStation 5, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, and Switch titles listed above can be purchased through Japanese <a title="Platforms > PlayStation [49,687 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation">PlayStation</a> Network and <a title="Platforms > Nintendo [23,696 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo">Nintendo</a> accounts using prepaid cards:</p><ul><li>PlayStation Store cards (yen): <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-1100-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/70dc0b?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,100</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-3000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/%20-card-5000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk4?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-10000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk3?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10,000</a></li><li>Nintendo eShop cards (yen): <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-1000-yen-japan-account/13/704a2v?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-1500-yen-japan-account/13/70cte9?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,500</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-3000-yen-japan-account/13/704a2w?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-5000-yen-japan-account/13/705239?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-9000-yen-japan-account/13/70bkw5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">9,000</a></li></ul><blockquote><p>Additionally, direct top-ups for gacha games are available <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/14/7133p?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>, including:</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/blue_protocol:_star_resonance/14/713bp?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Blue Protocol: Star Resonance</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/genshin_impact/14/7133t?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Genshin Impact</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/honkai_star_rail/14/7133z?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Honkai: Star Rail</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/love_and_deepspace/14/7134n?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Love and Deepspace</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/marvel_rivals/14/7134t?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Marvel Rivals</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/love_and_deepspace/14/7134n?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Where Winds Meet</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/zenless_zone_zero/14/7134z?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Zenless Zone Zero</em></a></li></ul></blockquote><h2><span>Demos, DLC, Updates, etc.</span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > DAVE THE DIVER [16 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dave-the-diver">DAVE THE DIVER</a></em> Downloadable Content “In the Jungle” (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, PS4, Xbox One, Switch, PC)</li><li><em>Echoes of Aincraft: Sword Art Online</em> Demo (PS5, Xbox Series, PC)</li><li><em><a title="Games > Edge of Memories [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/edge-of-memories">Edge of Memories</a></em> Demo (PC)</li><li><em><a title="Games > Hunter x Hunter: Nen x Impact [30 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/hunter-x-hunter-nen-x-impact">Hunter x Hunter: Nen x Impact</a></em> Downloadable Content Character Zeno (PS5, Switch, PC)</li><li><em><a title="Games > Sea of Thieves [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/sea-of-thieves">Sea of Thieves</a></em> “Season 20: Custom Seas” Update (PS5, Xbox Series, Xbox One, PC)</li><li><em><a title="Games > Until Then [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/until-then">Until Then</a></em> Downloadable Content “Afterimages” (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch, PC)</li><li><em>Zenless Zone Zero</em> Version 3.0 Update “A Sleepwalker’s Confession” (PS5, Xbox Series, PC, iOS, Android)</li></ul></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/06/this-weeks-japanese-game-releases-the-adventures-of-elliot-the-millennium-tales-more]]></content:encoded>
